c=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師出面唔好再jer住前線啦！！<br />\n民間記者會呢條戰線要人呀！！"},{"pid":"cf75c8a25f56ad6e45d3e1ddd941942bc5e1f289","tid":1419313,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:19:40.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"6216bf48aa06b1e8e5aa0d62b0f99c5c20029470","tid":1419313,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:20:29.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"6d7bac257d0cfc74a36cfdb72d6aa2781ae67802","tid":1419313,"uid":130907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"之後會安排在4點後播放？<br />\n<br />\n可以逐點反駁政府謬論"},{"pid":"9e3dd146a4d9c105b46d9f1ce45ca82f72c63e68","tid":1419313,"uid":266562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:24:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d05b624f10263eb0100fdb25567308197eba1862","tid":1419313,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:24:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4482050790b80eeb4f65a56d7316540c2d96c47e","tid":1419313,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3371f7ee06bd71c69280572d00cf59687c5365b","tid":1419313,"uid":89320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:34:09.000Z","msg":"唔好齋推唔諗呀！！<br />\n好重要呀！！！<br />\n出面有人真係會斷章取義屈義士亂打人架！<br />\n好多呢啲片喺Whatsapp group流傳！<br />\n<br />\n我諗其中一樣要喺記者會度提及嘅<br />\n就係呢啲容易畀人誤會嘅位<br />\n明明係廢老藍絲郁手<br />\n對家有心淨係報廢老畀人制服咗個柒樣<br />\n營造到好似係無辜畀打咁<br />\n真係有一堆好懶嘅盲毛會信<br />\n<br />\n對游離派嚟講<br />\n一建立咗「義士亂打人」呢個形象<br />\n就好難返轉頭 對家就會打蛇隨棍上<br />\n「義士」-&gt;「示威者」-&gt;「暴徒」<br />\n真係有呢個可能！！<br />\n真係唔好對民意don't give a shit<br />\n<br />\n趁而家對家仲係起步<br />\n我地快啲行動"},{"pid":"9945016a12d62ccd8e2d06502c95037ba55df6ea","tid":1419313,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr